---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About This Archive — The Collected Works of Rowan Black">
  <div class="info-page">
    <nav class="info-nav">
      <a href="/" class="info-back">← Archive</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="info-wrap">
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-label">About This Archive</div>
        <p class="info-text">This is a recovery project. The texts collected here were written over a period of roughly twenty-three years by Rowan Black. They were not published, submitted, or distributed by the author in any organized way. They were left behind.</p>
        <p class="info-text">The Corvids Collective began as an informal network of readers who, starting around 2011, independently encountered Black's writing in used bookstores, library donations, online forums, and other unlikely places. The recognition that these scattered pieces belonged to a single body of work led to the effort to find, preserve, and make them accessible.</p>
        <p class="info-text">Some pieces arrived intact. Some were damaged, incomplete, or fragmentary. All are presented here in the condition they were found, with brief annotations where context may be useful.</p>
        <p class="info-text">The archive is ongoing. If you believe you've encountered writing by Rowan Black and would consider contributing to the collection, please contact us at <a href="mailto:corvids@whoisrowanblack.com">corvids@whoisrowanblack.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .info-page { background: #eef0f4; min-height: 100vh; }
  .info-nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 1000;
    background: rgba(238,240,244,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    padding: 0 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; height: 48px;
  }
  .info-back {
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500;
    color: #2a6dd4; text-decoration: none;
    padding: 6px 16px; background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border-radius: 5px;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  }
  .info-wrap { max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 96px 16px 120px; }
  .info-card {
    background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
    padding: 36px;
  }
  .info-label {
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: #9099a8;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .info-text {
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8;
    color: #1a1d24; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .info-text:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .info-text a { color: #2a6dd4; text-decoration: none; }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .info-nav { padding: 0 12px; height: 44px; }
    .info-back { font-size: 12px; padding: 5px 12px; }
    .info-wrap { padding: 60px 0 80px; }
    .info-card { border-radius: 0; border-left: none; border-right: none; padding: 24px 16px; }
    .info-text { font-size: 13px; }
  }
</style>
